Concord Hotel and Suites in Parklands, Nairobi held its inaugural wine tasting event last Friday organised by Marie Pierre Kenya.Sommelier Geoffrey Kariuki took the guests through a a tasting journey of 13 different wines from France, Chile, Germany and South Africa.Present were Eatout business development manager Nafisa Fazal and Mental Health Awareness Centre founder Eva Kanyang onda.Eva Kanyang'onda founder of Mental Health Awreness Centre.The sample wines to be tasted.Ian Ashcroft and Helen Wacera from Casks &amp; Barrels.Raj Malde and Sajel Malde both from Mjengo Limited.The Sommelier at the wine tasting event at Concord Hotel.